name: DGradeMix
description:
It's a mix made by an idiot who slapped things together and decided it's good enough to upload after generating 20000 images with it.

I've mainly used it to generate cute images, because I like cute images. Can it do other stuff?
I dunno. Probably. It can do some weird stuff.

All the images posted here have been SD Upscaled to showcase whatever.

Probably best used with a VAE of your liking.

The VAE that I use is vae-ft-mse-840000-ema-pruned

Here's an example prompting style that I have found great success with, but you do what you want.

(game cg), highres, (masterpiece), (best quality), official art, hdr,
